metadata.name: A Day to Remember
metadata.description:
It was a day to remember for all the visitors of La Gran Capilla de la Renaissance Digitale. 
Everyone trying to understand why there's so much innocent blood being spilled for the GREED of one person. 
Innocent anons standing in shock as everything crumbles around them...some took revenge upon their favorite "Influencers"
Some say that people are still trying to get their funds out, just to get a disappointing red message back that reads... NO CASH 

Let me take you down on a private tour of this magnificent chapel...full of art, history & mystery
